description: The SPDR Dow Jones Industrial AverageSM ETF Trust seeks to provide investment results that, before expenses, correspond generally to the price and yield performance of the Dow Jones Industrial AverageSM (the “Index”)The Dow Jones Industrial AverageSM (DJIA) is composed of 30 “blue-chip” U.S. stocksThe DJIA is the oldest continuous barometer of the U.S. stock market, and the most widely quoted indicator of U.S. stock market activityThe DJIA is a price weighted index of 30 component common stocks
name: SPDR Dow Jones Industrial Average ETF Trust
